
Nitrogen version 2.0.x

---

Nitrogen relies on the following software:

  - Erlang R13B02 or later (http://erlang.org)

  - Rebar - Erlang build tool.
    Hg Repo:  http://bitbucket.org/basho/rebar
    

  - SimpleBridge - Common interface to Erlang HTTP servers.
    Git Repo: git://github.com/rklophaus/SimpleBridge.git
    Commit:   652a3d1

  - coverize - Erlang coverage analysis.
    Git Repo: git://github.com/mmullis/coverize.git
    Commit:   860452d

  - mochiweb - HTTP Server
    SVN Repo: http://mochiweb.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/
    Revision: 133

  - yaws - HTTP Server
    http://yaws.hyber.org/download/yaws-1.87.tar.gz

---

Javascript Libraries:
  - JQuery 1.3.2
  - JQuery UI 1.7
  - Live Validation 1.3

---


---

Nitrogen is built and tested on a Mac running OSX Leopard.
